    <div class="col col-sm-5">
      <h4>MS Biorepository Samples Data Dashboard</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="col col-sm-7"><p class="text-center" style="padding-left:50px;font-size:10pt;">Click an element to remove subjects with that phenotype from all graphs and study participant counts. To restore, click the faint grey value in the graph's legend, or click "Reset Dashboard" to restore all graphs.</p></div>
